python3 ftpbrute.py --help

Argument	Description	Default
-t, --target	Target hostname or IP address	Required
-p, --port	Port number	21
-U, --users	Username wordlist file	Required (unless resuming)
-P, --passwords	Password wordlist file	Required (unless resuming)
-T, --threads	Number of concurrent threads	20
--ftp	Use standard FTP protocol	Default
--ftps	Use FTPS (SSL/TLS)	
--ftpes	Use FTPES (Explicit SSL)	
--sftp	Use SFTP protocol	
--timeout	Connection timeout in seconds	8
--rate-limit	Max requests per second	0 (unlimited)
--resume	Resume previous scan session	
--encrypt	Encrypt results with random key	
-v, --verbose	Enable verbose output	
